[[Image:thingsfallapart.jpg|thumb|''Things Fall Apart'', Anchor trade paperback cover]]'''Chinua Achebe''' bu onye dere akwu-kwo onye Igbo. O bu ya dere akwu-kwo ana-kpo ''Things Fall Apart''. Nka bu nke asi ma ya ukwu ebe ala ndi bekee. Obula onye diplomat na government [[Biafra]], 1967 ru 1970.

Amuru Chinua Achebe, November 16, 1930 ebe Ogidi, Naigeria, a guzie ya ''Albert Chinualumogu Achebe''. Ma 1948 ru 1953, ha study-e English n'ebe University of Ibadan. Mgbe Achebe dere akwu-kwo ya, a akwu-kwo ahu rere 10 million (nde) copies, ha translate ya na 50 languages (asusu).

